"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![Source: https://decrypt.co/](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zJNZibn5BNr7XksBM0ojE.png?height=450&width=800)\\n\\nNFTs are more than JPEGS. They are community-builders, value-distributors and overall a new way of supporting/benefiting from highly valuable creative works. And we want to support that.\\n\\n### Who are we?\\n\\n[Flair.Finance](https://flair.finance/) is a decentralized Escrow & Launchpad for NFT-based projects.\\n\\nWe built Flair to help value creators and developers to responsibility raise funds and supporters to safely back them up on their ideas. Our platform helps NFT-based projects to launch within minutes with no technical knowledge.\\n\\nWe’re on a mission to find the best projects and teams out there, support them with all the technical necessities, provide them cash and capital, and help them bring their ideas to life. If you’re here for the long-term and want to create next valuable project, come[ talk to us](https://twitter.com/FlairFinance).\\n\\n### What are we looking for?\\n\\n* Creative people in the fields of music, animation, gaming, etc. that can prove their record with previous efforts and achievements\\n* Be interested in new web3 space and eager to explore NFTs as way to raise funding and also build a community around your work/project\\n* Already have a community/audience or be willing to work on building it\\n\\n### What are we offering?\\n\\n* We are offering a grant up to 2ETH for selected applicants\\n* We will help with all the technical aspect of launching your NFT campaign\\n* We will offer marketing/community building support\\n\\n### Want to apply?\\n\\nPlease fill and submit the form below. We will get back to you shortly (within a week)\\n\\n[https://forms.gle/BmBufs262Wf7jzpU6](https://forms.gle/BmBufs262Wf7jzpU6)\\n\\n[https://forms.gle/BmBufs262Wf7jzpU6](https://forms.gle/BmBufs262Wf7jzpU6)\\n\\n### Useful Links\\n\\n**Platform:** <https://flair.finance/>\\n\\n**Docs:** <https://docs.flair.finance/>\\n\\n**Team:** <https://flair.finance/#/team>\\n\\n**FAQ:** <https://docs.flair.finance/getting-started/faq>\\n\\n**Discord:** <https://discord.gg/flair>\\n\\n**Twitter:** <https://twitter.com/FlairFinance>\",\"timestamp\":1640249188,\"title\":\"Funding Ideas of Tomorrow\"},\"digest\":\"k52u3hm1zP11J0ya9OlPxoXrC8H4cEAFN9mg0WTsGis\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1350fb6f2f4D6955970af6E44f7cD31E01b68663\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Z39JBo7NDUbFQrMCPrMCMjuwD3FVqoQ6nUK9BMWPUD0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"6Xhw9L3eQrWfJR4ZAy83x4I_wGToNbQ_PedPzRavqIk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"r-us1C9AINSFC44Yj_npx2w4Xo78gv20Slil-io9Qjk_vjVX2PjJuojVGFDSdxP1jmMIBtNhcC2qqUbeosAapQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdb31fa3c10605d1eff28bcff05b4ad11129800058fbf61c34f30ac292a59a6db7bb4a0b44c2a5484995a0ee94c864e7547c7387f50327f538a99b5be631d9c411b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Z39JBo7NDUbFQrMCPrMCMjuwD3FVqoQ6nUK9BMWPUD0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"6Xhw9L3eQrWfJR4ZAy83x4I_wGToNbQ_PedPzRavqIk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"k52u3hm1zP11J0ya9OlPxoXrC8H4cEAFN9mg0WTsGis\"}"